# MedVirtual Meta Creative Handoff

Default priority: **Virtual Medical Admin direct-response ads + animated video** production clarity.

## Goal
Keep bold VMA static + video ads in the hopper. Make “do this next” obvious for graphics in under two minutes.

## Brand
- Ad-facing: **MedVirtual** only (never MedVirtual.ai)
- Font: Be Vietnam
- Active Meta colors: lime / yellow / cobalt / cyan / vivid green / commercial red / black / white / deep navy / MedVirtual teal
- **No pink** (other buyer territory)

## Service model
Hire dedicated full-time virtual staff who join the practice team.
Not a call center / managed front desk / software / chatbot / AI service.

## Visual DNA
**Current:** High-contrast human-led “Hire a Virtual Medical Admin” — huge headline · generic professional admin · 3–4 benefits · price/trust badges (pending approval) · mobile-first.
Animated: Remotion + CapCut templates from the same concept data.

## Removed from active site (July 2026)
Named Real People / Talent Pool profile ads · Role-Offer hire boards · SaaS glassmorphism / no-people primary.
Archive only: `_archive/july-2026-removed/`. History notes collapsed on Approved Creative / Dashboard.

## Files
- Public: web-safe handoff assets
- `.local-masters/`: huge video / .ai
- `_private/`: internal docs — never expose
- `_archive/`: removed historical directions

## Site order
Dashboard → Approved Creative → New Ad Ideas → Aspect Ratios → Competitor Wall → Animated Video → Prompts & Copy → Production Handoff

Current focus for designers: **see the four approved masters · generate 15–20 concepts · rebuild winners in Meta sizes**. Video after statics. Do not invent fake format previews.

Same header via `scripts/shared-doc-header.mjs`. Never style bare `details`/`summary` globally — scope to `main`.

## Claims
Do not invent HIPAA, rates, savings %, performance, or free offers. Pending claims are never launch-ready.
